Package: wxjlst3
Title: Cumulative Publication Analysis Toolkit
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jialin", "Wu", email = "wujialin@example.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: Provides automated analysis and visualization of academic 
    publication trends over time. Processes Excel-based citation data with 
    Chinese date formats, generates cumulative publication plots, and 
    supports bibliometric analysis. Features include automated year-range 
    detection, missing data handling, and publication-quality visualization 
    outputs.
